Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one year, in ten years, will anything change?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world I drew in the corner of my dreams,
