Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can blame this heart of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing is really correct!
